data.description: Stunning home in popular Summerlake, close enough to Disney to enjoy the nightly fireworks. 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathroom, a first floor office/den with double doors and an upstairs loft and a bonus room that could be easily converted to a 4th bedroom. The first floor, and all bathrooms have high end tile with a hardwood floor look. The gourmet kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and raised breakfast bar. Extended vanity in the master bath. Extended covered lanai with enlarged sliding glass door, leads out to a large fenced in back yard. Brand new AC system. Lawn service is included in the reasonable HOA which covers access to all the great amenities Summerlake offers. Resort Style Swimming Pool & Clubhouse, Fitness Center, Tennis & Basketball Courts, Volleyball, Walking Trails, Bike Path, Parks & Dog Parks Throughout. Excellent schools! Including Summerlake Elementary just three minutes away and rated among the top 5% in the state. Community is conveniently located near Disney World, Orange County National Golf Center, Downtown Historic Winter Garden, Shopping & Restaurants at Winter Garden Village, SR-429 SR-535, 408 and I-4.
